Description: Well hey everyone i spent 2 days on this and i know my 1st map gg_smallwar and gg_forts_barricade sucked
alot so i took the liberty in actaully trying my best and here i came up with a spacey middle with a dead hostage
boxes stacked on top of eachother to let you go on the wall to check if enemy is hiding behind it because i got
tired of walking there and not knowing a enemy is right behind you and get pwned in the head. So all in all its pretty
.. ill leave the blank spot up to you enjoy my map and remember comment and approve if you thinks its alright
